  ('hollow-body-hold', 'Use tuck hollow, elevated head support, or avoid prolonged supine holds if contraindicated; prioritize rib-pelvis stacking in side-lying or quadruped alternatives.', 'No sex-based default. Scale by trunk control, hip mobility, wrist tolerance, coordination, sport demand, and symptoms.'),
