  ('straddle-sit-reach-lift', 'Narrow straddle and hand support; avoid aggressive adductor stretch if symptomatic.', 'No sex-based default. Scale by trunk control, hip mobility, wrist tolerance, coordination, sport demand, and symptoms.'),
